 


		----->>>   CHANGELOG   <<<-----
		
		
Version 0.9.7-----------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------
( 12-08-2004 )

0)*  Project name acronym is changed to QBASystem, cause I noticed some
     commercial stuff named QBAS;

0)+  Changed temp files names in configure script. System is more modular;
     
0)*  Major change at the configure help option facilities. A new method 
     to output help message has been coded in configure script;

0)+  Readme change and improvement;

0)+  Added EXECUTE var to execute script code if OBJECT is ok;

0)+  Added possibility for option description at the configure help;



Version 0.9.6-----------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------
( 04-07-2004 )

0)+  Changes in the linkage scheme thanks to Peter Chang suggestions.
     Now "marked_static" option tryes the static linkage also on
     default paths before trying with shared. Added code to check
     lib existance if marked_static is set;
     
0)+  Changed option "--static-linking-path" in "--static-link" in configure 
     script. Not defining a path on this option will automatically define
     STATIC_LIBPATH = 1 in configure.def to make work the proper code
     for static linkage. Code of lib existance needs a speed-up although;

0)-  Corrected bug on output message thanks to Peter Chang;

0)-  Corrected bug on lib existance code ( wrong branch );




Version 0.9.5-----------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------
( 26-06-2004 )

0)-  Changed the "--includedir" option with "--dependency-dir"
     in configure script to avoid confusing with autoconf parameters;
     
0)+  Added option "--disable-warnings" in configure script;

0)+  Added PACKAGE feature: allow user to set custom paths
     for dependency checking and inclusion on PACKAGE;

0)-  Corrected bug on linkage;

0)+  Empowered linkage code and friendly output; 
     
     
     
     
Version 0.9.4 -----------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------
( 28-05-2004 )

0)-  Fixed a little output bug in 'check.qbas': when a certain
     FEATURE was defined more than one time, summary reported 
     more time the same line;
     
0)+  More code to "configure" script: help messages will show
     custom options now;
     
    


Version 0.9.3 -----------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------
( 18-04-2004 )

0)+  QBAS can create a 'config.h' file following directives 
     in build.definition and using 'config.h.in' as code base;
     
0)+  PROJECT_SETTINGS can handle option 'no_qt': support for 
     projects which not use Qt libs ( not working completely
     although ;-( );




Version 0.9.2 -----------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------
( 13-04-2004 )

0)+ Overwrite default values QMAKE_CXXFLAGS / QMAKE_CFLAGS / QMAKE_LFLAGS 
    if defined by user;

0)+ Added 'release' in CONFIG if debug is not set;

0)+ Made visible when skipping linkage;

0)+ Enabling features has become similar to what GNU tools do:
    --enable-FEATURE --disable-FEATURE;
    
0)+ Modified the output message code. Added possibility to use templates
    for friendly output messages; 




Version 0.9.1 -----------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------
( 29-03-2004 )

0)+ Added code to provide enable/disable of code blocks;

0)+ Added code to provide an user friendly resume summary
    output;
    
0)- Fixed bug about the QTDIR check;

0)+ Added code to be more detached from environment variables;

  


Version 0.9.0 -----------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------
( 29-02-2004 )

First public release;
